               <provenance>Walda Hāymānot and his parents, ʾƎlfǝyos and
                     Walatta Māryām, are mentioned as the donors in the supplication formulas
                     (interlineally, possible in a different hand) and in Additio 1. In addition,
                     names of other persons are inserted interlineally: Lǝya Dǝngǝl, Mazgaba
                     Śǝllāse, Walda Śǝllāse (e.g. 106va,
                     135ra).</provenance></history>
